{"tid":2173779,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"呂秉權：或首案實證中共統戰","createTime":"2020-08-25T12:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T12:38:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f28c6dedaa176830290bb9bf4d73ffc73115ad8","tid":2173779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/SURPA7MFTNGAVJEMJ7WDMBN6YY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FSURPA7MFTNGAVJEMJ7WDMBN6YY%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXdT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=598ce68b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FSURPA7MFTNGAVJEMJ7WDMBN6YY%2F&h=0dc6b9d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/SURPA7MFTNGAVJEMJ7WDMBN6YY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n呂秉權：或首案實證中共統戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6HpTN1lks8pIMlviofiLw1hE2D8=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ENXGVJXZFBHAXD7P22QIMYURYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6HpTN1lks8pIMlviofiLw1hE2D8%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FENXGVJXZFBHAXD7P22QIMYURYY.jpg&h=e6058e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美雙面諜一案，揭發中共透過收買及拉攏手段策反海外民運人士。浸大新聞系高級講師呂秉權（圖）形容，今次或是首宗具實質證據證明中共情報手段的案件。他認為香港現正處於中美角力的前沿，加上國安法賦予不受法律約束的權力，在港的類似滲透工作，未來只會有過之而無不及。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籲港人勿為「捉鬼」失互信<br />\n<br />\n呂指六四事件後逃亡而形成的海外民運圈子，一直被國安及統戰部門視為重點工作對象，「近年北京將『外國勢力』改稱『外部勢力』，就。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港政圈和社運界經常陷於「捉鬼」的兩難迷思，呂秉權認為香港的形勢複雜，既有。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n滲透防不勝防，呂秉權認為雖然防人之心不可無，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"866d9333bc9d18a61899fd5d69c3bcddf2f69ee7","tid":2173779,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"差呢拎"},{"pid":"62be501770